SORRY YOU MISSED IT Access the recording below
Image Businesswoman showing doctor something on tablet
We’re sorry we missed you at our recent webinar on the results of the 2022 Telehealth Benchmark Survey, conducted in association with Becker’s Hospital Review.
We recorded the presentation and have it available for you to access anytime! Feel free to watch, share and reach out to us to discuss these findings and see how connected care can seamlessly integrate into your organization.
